夜開始有在場人仕 叫出「死曱甴」「暴徒」「唔讀書」<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n例句: 1. 唔知班「死曱甴」「暴徒」有冇出黎投票<br />\n          2. 「死曱甴」 投黎到冇用<br />\n<br />\n目的: 挑引在場人仕，由其而家將年青身份證分另一條隊排。  警方會將「擾亂」分子拘捕，姐係將成條Y/Z身份證 既人拉哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n下一步: 另一方陣營係大拘捕之後用旅遊巴將一車車既選民推去投票站<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>大家記住，你今日角色係一個廢老廢青，只投建制派，所有野都聽唔到，睇唔到。</strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong>「我真係外賣仔黎架」</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果仲未明，請睇完一次「演員的自我修養」先好出去投票<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebf423bf0aa0aad99d2be2a9a0b451be16b379f5","tid":1749594,"uid":184099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T04:34:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c517e6a267057971b175172ae5c86ecc8d682e99","tid":1749594,"uid":184099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T04:34:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fb9cf5839723735ec22d396df7b71a9e93b29f97","tid":1749594,"uid":184099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T04:35:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3ce2a22c32422bc9db76bc6ba7193da33ccec673","tid":1749594,"uid":184099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T04:35:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b5db8865ac6cdb47e3501d9cb742f9e6ef274c63","tid":1749594,"uid":184099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T04:38:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"451aea6c34fbdfda619e0bd683cb8035c5c1589a","tid":1749594,"uid":184099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T04:39:09.000Z","msg":"推"}]}